{"tid":565430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[公關災難]拉闊style fb page抄襲而唔認數","createTime":"2018-02-19T03:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T03:40:27.000Z","uid":164467,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0bde65ecbe7b03aa6f04d870682f49922627931b","tid":565430,"uid":164467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T03:40:27.000Z","msg":"剛才睇完隔離個post講緊公關災難<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 若果一間鋪頭搵個非禮犯做代言，你地覺得有冇問題？</span><br />\n<br />\n一上fb, 又發現另一個公關災難<br />\n<br />\n事源有個細page講述年宵後好多垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/112231_b25bf2f4960d2536f8272e9c819a20da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F112231_b25bf2f4960d2536f8272e9c819a20da.png&h=2b0b6edf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/112234_24c0b1926e4baf5d124c4ad21687b35e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F112234_24c0b1926e4baf5d124c4ad21687b35e.png&h=0bb28f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出文時間 03:00 </span><br />\n<br />\n過左幾個鐘後，另一fb page出現同一篇文章<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/112413_0c1bfd6d1e37d1c52ae0dc6c7051fd83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F112413_0c1bfd6d1e37d1c52ae0dc6c7051fd83.png&h=4f631bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/112417_4e8df64178964dfcecbb77179e3a6716.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F112417_4e8df64178964dfcecbb77179e3a6716.png&h=9b7643fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出文時間 10:00 </span><br />\n<br />\n當事人（拉闊style) 被質疑後回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/112555_0d120370f66b468bc7755a79286af6b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F112555_0d120370f66b468bc7755a79286af6b1.png&h=7a37cc41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/112557_c1906a2d9a61bc11d2e0a42151139de3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F112557_c1906a2d9a61bc11d2e0a42151139de3.png&h=f147ae23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢類事件真係好奇怪，被人質疑是否有抄襲問題但個態度咁撚樣，好似係到講「我抄咗又點，你咬我食呀？」。<br />\n被質疑嘅page like數近十萬，而被抄襲嘅page只有一萬多少少。若果真係抄襲，相信只會令多like嘅page更多人like。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話讚100毛，同樣都係content farm，周圍搵資料出文抄襲，但起碼都有出返source。<br />\n<br />\n利申，非當事人，但睇到個comment好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}